metadata.name: He Matapihi Ki Toku Wairua
metadata.description:
A Window to my Soul 
(pron. Hair ma-ta-peehee key tore-ku why-roo-ah

Anxiety, sadness, fear and doubt. 
Emotions I know too well. 
Neither friend nor foe, they are the cell mates that share this lonely room with me, existing only to hold me in a place I once was, a feeling, I once had.

They blanket me, weighted down under a sea of darkness, they keep me here, imprisoned in my own head, hands pushing down upon my shoulders.

I need air. 
Open the window.

Ko taku NFT tuatahi tenei
This is my very first NFT
